# HearYourVOICE — environment
#
# Copy to `.env` in your project root and fill in what you actually need.
# `.env` is gitignored. NEVER commit real keys, and never paste one into a chat log.
#
# You do NOT need any of this to run the free paths:
#   research · script · punchline debate · storyboard · shotlist
#   gen-voiceover.mjs --emit-md   (TTS sheet to voice anywhere)
#   veo-generate.py --emit-md     (prompts to generate anywhere)
# Keys are only needed when YOU decide to spend.

# ── Voiceover (phase 2) — only if generating with ElevenLabs ──────────────────
# Get one at https://elevenlabs.io → Profile → API Keys
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=
# Pick a voice at https://elevenlabs.io/app/voice-library and paste its id
VOICE_ID=
MODEL=eleven_v3
FORMAT=mp3_44100_128

# ── Generative footage (phase 4) — only if generating clips ───────────────────
# Optional. Most videos never need this: graphics + self-shot + Creative-Commons
# cover them, and generative is the most expensive step in the whole skill.
# Point these at YOUR provider plugin — this skill ships no provider.
VEO_PLUGIN_PATH=
VEO_AGENT_ROOT=
VEO_MODEL=
# Estimate rate only — shown in the cost gate before you approve a spend.
VEO_PRICE_PER_SEC_THB=30
